      "options": {
        "content": "## Graphyard Overview\n\n- Datasource: `Graphyard InfluxDB`\n- Measurement: `graphyard_metrics`\n- Query language: `InfluxQL`\n- Host metrics from Vector use metric names prefixed with `host.`\n\nUse the **host** filter at the top to focus charts. Room temperature and infrastructure/device temperature are shown in separate panels.\n",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.0",
      "title": "Graphyard Quick Start",
      "type": "text"
    },
